name: TemPsy-Report
body:
Welcome to TemPsy-Report
==========

TemPsy-Report is a tool for collecting violation information from a faulty execution trace that is in violation of [*TemPsy* properties](https://github.com/weidou/TemPsy-Check#properties). The tool has been developed by [Wei Dou](http://people.svv.lu/dou), at the [SVV lab](http://www.svv.lu) of the [University of Luxembourg](http://wwwen.uni.lu).
